# Cline Memory Bank Rules

## Auto-read on session start
When a new session starts, automatically read:
1. projectbrief.md - Understand project goals
2. activeContext.md - Know current focus
3. progress.md - Check completion status

## Update triggers
Update memory bank when:
- Task completed → progress.md + activeContext.md
- Architecture changed → systemPatterns.md
- New feature added → productContext.md + progress.md
- Blocker identified → activeContext.md

## File hierarchy
projectbrief.md → productContext.md, systemPatterns.md, techContext.md → activeContext.md → progress.md
